# sqs-demo


Configure aws credential file to connect to SQS

sample configure

```text
[default]
output                    = json
region                    = us-east-1
aws_assumed_role_arn      = arn:aws:iam::12345656546:role/myAccount
aws_credential_expiration = 2023-02-18T18:09:10Z
aws_access_key_id         = ASIA5ONH7WM4FVQJ8YFB
aws_secret_access_key     = QbXdfDmTJp96rWUE/m5qdlVm7iwZhJNwvdxtJslD
aws_session_token         = 
```
